  "title": "MultiLineActionBar",
  "description": "Multi-line text support for action bar.",
  "body": "# MultiLineActionBar\nThis is a simple client-side mod that adds support for multi-line text for action bar. This text will be centered relative to the Vanilla's text offset.\n\nUse `\\n` for new line, like this:\n\n```\n/title @s actionbar {\"text\":\"Line1\\nLine2\"}\n```\n\n## Without mod\n[<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/diskree/MultiLineActionBar/1.20%2B/screenshots/vanilla.jpg\"/>](https://modrinth.com/modpack/achievetodo)\n\n## With mod\n[<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/diskree/MultiLineActionBar/1.20%2B/screenshots/multilineactionbar.jpg\"/>](https://modrinth.com/modpack/achievetodo)\n",
